    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and looks as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless, displaying a deep, mirror-like finish with no chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather and trim showing zero signs of wear and still carrying that new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been kept in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships. This is a rare find for a collector or a discerning buyer who demands the very best.",
